column3: “Picked up this stuff from NILE COLLECTIVE in Venice. had a great strong smell with loads of crystals!”

“I've never had a sativa that made me want to go on more adventures than this strain. Very uplifting, happy, and creative. It's about 25% thc so the high will definitely creep up. Good to smoke with friends!”

“Picked some up from Nile collective, and I must say, this is an amazing sativa. Never have I felt so focused from any strain. That is, until I tried this one. Definite day-time strain, but you can still go to sleep with it. I highly recommend this strain, especially good for work.”
“i start laughing whenever i smoked that strain..super potent og..”
“was the shit”
“I love love love this strain. I want to make love to Venice OG while on Venice OG.”

“Just picked this up and I have to say I'm pretty happy with it so far. The buds are a nice size, very leafy with a lot of purple and even some red. Strong sativa effects, definitely won't smoke this at night, but have to say I'm pretty stoked to smoke it and get some work done. Definitely worth trying it out, better than a lot of other sativas I've tried.”
“i suggested this to one of my homie and he get an ounce.. and that was the wise choice..”
“up n a way”
“psychedelic, happy strong high..def. one of the greatest og's”
“i suggested this to one of my homie and he get an ounce.. and that was the wise choice..”

“Tried for level 8 headache. Didn't drop the pain down as much as I'd hope, but made me not care about it. The tingly feeling that comes with it is fun and relieving to a certain extent. Makes my feet and hands very cold, so cold others notice so it isn't just a sensation. Since head is bad, I do want to drop the pain enough to sleep. While I don't feel knocked out and definitely can get stuff done, this doesn't keep ...”
“Great strain!!! Picked up from my dealer in Texas. Great head buzz”
“went surfing after.”

“I really enjoyed the high that this strain gives. The bud itself has a beautiful look. Sativa strains are my favorite, and this one is among those special strains. It fades you but at the same time you are sharp and aware of time.”

“Super bomb buds! This bud doesn't make me feel lethargic, rather  quite the opposite. I can complete all my daily tasks but still be on a good fade. If you find this strain at your local dispensary, I highly suggest you pick some up and give it a try. You won't be disappointed!”

“Delicous, piney. Tastes like chemdawg, urkle, Flo, oaxacan and thai purple sativas with some Sour Diesel and SF Valley OG Kush highlights... Def has some himalayan kush as well as kashmiri leaf formations. So bomb!!!”
“The VOG is excellent for all day , get you through the day , and keep you feeling great medicine.”

“musky smell, large orange hairs
calyx to leaf: 8
good piney taste.”
“One of my favorites. Strong uplifting head high. Reduces moderate to severe pain while allowing me to work.”
“Nice taste with a very daytimey high, quite delightful.”
“really really nice daytime strain..”
“one of the strongest I've had in a while definitely a pick-me-upper wonderful flavor too”

“nice nugs.clean smell.
calyx to leaf: 8
fat orange hairs”
“great high but it makes me so exhausted which is odd because it's sativa. overall though it's a great high but it's nothing new.”
“Rolled 2 fat blunts of em In my car, I seriously I so baked.. But yeah great high lots of fun”

“Listen OK usually I go in for compassion and normally there very cool with that but recently they told me next time you come you donate 5 I'm like OK yeah I over did myself, today though I brought in 5 for a compassion sack and they denied me I asked why they didn't answer I told them I had money showed them and they told me to leave and I was escorted by security out”
